 the\nLovelock gravity, are discussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 22 May 2009 07:45:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 28 Nov 2009 19:10:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2010-04-30"}
