 discuss the case of Majorana neutrino magnetic moment. It is\npointed out that spin flips may quickly equilibrate electron neutrinos with\nnon-electron antineutrinos if mu_Majorana~10^{-12}mu_B. This may lead to\nvarious consequences for supernova physics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 22 May 2009 10:37:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 1 Aug 2009 06:59:54 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 19 Aug 2009 10:48:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-11-20"}
